<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 21:13:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴西媒体报道，前巴西总统鲁塞夫在上海住院。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/ex-brazil-president-rousseff-hospitalized-shanghai-brazilian-media-reports-2025-02-24/</link><description>巴西报纸Folha de sao Paulo周一报道说，前巴西总统迪尔玛·鲁塞夫（Dilma Rousseff）现在在上海住院。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 20:22:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/ex-brazil-president-rousseff-hospitalized-shanghai-brazilian-media-reports-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者瞄准中国的贸易惯例</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-take-aim-chinas-trade-practices-2025-02-24/</link><description>周一，两党议员团体正在提出立法，以加强美国的贸易执法法，并解决对中国的腰带和道路倡议的新担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 20:07:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-take-aim-chinas-trade-practices-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>USTR提议向中国船只收取高达150万美元的收费，以进入美国港口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/ustr-proposes-charging-chinese-ships-up-15-million-enter-us-ports-2025-02-24/</link><description>美国贸易代表办公室已提议为进入美国港口的中国建造的船只收取高达150万美元的费用，这是对中国对全球造船，海上和物流部门日益增长的统治的调查的一部分。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 20:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/ustr-proposes-charging-chinese-ships-up-15-million-enter-us-ports-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>古巴的顶级雪茄制造商中断记录，销售额为8.27亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/cubas-top-cigarmaker-breaks-record-with-sales-827-million-2024-2025-02-24/</link><description>古巴最高的雪茄制造商哈巴诺斯（Habanos）周一表示，由于收入来自中国和亚洲其他地方的快速增长市场，该公司豪华烟的销售额在2024年达到了创纪录的8.27亿美元。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 19:04:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/cubas-top-cigarmaker-breaks-record-with-sales-827-million-2024-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：印度的2月黄金进口量以创纪录的高价达到20年低点。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-feb-gold-imports-hit-20-year-low-record-high-prices-sources-say-2025-02-24/</link><description>一名政府官员和三位银行经销商告诉路透社，印度的黄金进口量将从一年前的水平从一年前的水平降低到20年的最低水平，从而将其降至20年来最低，而需求量减少了，这将使印度的黄金进口量为85％。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 16:54:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-feb-gold-imports-hit-20-year-low-record-high-prices-sources-say-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>彭博新闻报道，特斯拉准备在中国部署完整的自动驾驶功能。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-prepares-deploy-full-self-driving-features-china-bloomberg-news-reports-2025-02-24/</link><description>彭博社新闻报道，特斯拉正在为中国的客户提供软件更新，以提供类似于美国的全部自动驾驶（FSD）功能的驾驶辅助功能。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 13:50:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-prepares-deploy-full-self-driving-features-china-bloomberg-news-reports-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>英国总理说，G7应该承担更多的风险来挤压俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/british-pm-says-g7-should-be-ready-take-more-risk-2025-02-24/</link><description>英国首相凯尔·斯特默（Keir Starmer）周一表示，七个（G7）富裕国家的组织应该愿意在对俄罗斯入侵乌克兰的制裁方面承担更大的风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 11:32:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/british-pm-says-g7-should-be-ready-take-more-risk-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>早上出价：当德国中盖激增时，云聚集在墙壁上</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-02-24/</link><description>看看美国和迈克·多兰（Mike Dolan）的全球市场的前一天</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 11:24:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：特朗普援助冻结墨西哥港口的反毒品计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/trump-aid-freeze-disrupts-anti-narcotics-program-mexican-ports-2025-02-24/</link><description>据八名熟悉情况，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的外国援助冻结使墨西哥的一项联合国计划停滞不前，旨在阻止进口的芬太尼化学药品到达该国的毒品卡特尔。这是墨西哥的几项美国国际机构努力之一，最近几周被停车命令脱轨。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 11:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/trump-aid-freeze-disrupts-anti-narcotics-program-mexican-ports-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国的Shimao以11美元的近海债务改造获得了债权人的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-shimao-secures-creditor-backing-11-bln-offshore-debt-revamp-2025-02-24/</link><description>中国房地产开发商Shimao集团已确保债权人的支持，以重组约110.4亿美元的离岸债务，这是多年的流动性麻烦之后，该行业的最新交易。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 11:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-shimao-secures-creditor-backing-11-bln-offshore-debt-revamp-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国的习近平在乌克兰战争周年纪念日中与普京的“无限制”伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/xi-putin-hold-phone-call-ukraine-war-anniversary-state-media-says-2025-02-24/</link><description>中国媒体在与俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）的电话中，在俄罗斯全面入侵乌克兰的三周年纪念日报道，中国总统习近平在与俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京的电话中确认了他的“无限制”伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 10:35:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/xi-putin-hold-phone-call-ukraine-war-anniversary-state-media-says-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/illegal-us-vape-sales-worth-least-24-billion-2024-data-shows-2025-02-24/</link><description>根据路透社审查的私人零售销售数据，美国未经授权的一次性一次性vapes的销售额约为2024年的24亿美元，或者来自诸如便利店和超市等商店的电子烟的35％。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 10:30:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/illegal-us-vape-sales-worth-least-24-billion-2024-data-shows-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>CATL大众汽车在中国合作锂电池开发</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-catl-collaborate-china-lithium-battery-development-2025-02-24/</link><description>CATL周一说，大众集团的中国子公司和全球最大的电池制造商CATL计划合作开发大众汽车在中国电动汽车的锂电池。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 09:20:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-catl-collaborate-china-lithium-battery-development-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>骗局中心镇压之后，泰国山区边界上的数千人处于困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-limbo-thai-myanmar-border-after-scam-centre-crackdown-2025-02-24/</link><description>三名消息人士周一告诉路透社，成千上万的外国人从缅甸的在线骗局运营中心被释放在与泰国边界的边界上，在对犯罪团伙经营的化合物的跨国镇压之后。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 07:47:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-limbo-thai-myanmar-border-after-scam-centre-crackdown-2025-02-24/</guid></item><item><title>国家以2000亿美元的自然金融协议进行新的尝试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/countries-make-fresh-attempt-200-billion-nature-finance-deal-2025-02-24/</link><description>本周的各国聚集在罗马，第二次裂开，弄清楚如何每年产生2000亿美元以帮助维护世界的生物多样性 - 并随着美国的回归而射击全球合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 07:07:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/countries-make-fresh-attempt-200-billion-nature-finance-deal-2025-02-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>